<br>
The Efreeti Belt is a drop from any of the three Efreetis in the zone. Dojorn would be your best bet...<br>
<br>
The Wind Tablet is a drop from the bixie boss of bee island, whom I will not attempt to spell the name of.<br>
<br>
Given the way the Air quests work, the &quot;common&quot; items are then drops from the two previous islands. So the Spiroc Wind Totem is an uncommon drop from Spiroc island, and the Pegasus Statuette is an uncommon drop from Pegasus island.<br>
<br>
Amanita<br>
